rows.label: qst105701_msg0001
rows.name:
Listen, friends, listen!
Big news afoot!

rows.label: qst105701_msg0002
rows.name:
Was looking through correspondences
of Bahn, and found shocking thing!

rows.label: qst105701_msg0004
rows.name:
In addition to ordinary dealings
recorded in Avaritia Guild accounts...

rows.label: qst105701_msg0005
rows.name:
These documents listing mysterious
movements of money!

rows.label: qst105701_msg0006
rows.name:
And after further investigate, me
notice on days of money transfer...

rows.label: qst105701_msg0007
rows.name:
Always undocumented ship passing
through Avaritia!

rows.label: qst105701_msg0008
rows.name:
Nilny very thorough Nopon.
Managed to track down pilot of ship.

rows.label: qst105701_msg0009
rows.name:
Even obtained confession that ship
transporting cash to Liberalitas!

rows.label: qst105701_msg0010
rows.name:
Oh, yes! Nilny not agent of
Special Audit Bureau for nothing.

rows.label: qst105701_msg0011
rows.name:
But would like help of friends to
find exactly where Bahn money
went and what it used for.

rows.label: qst105701_msg0013
rows.name:
It seem money was taken to Island Base
Lindwurm. Small island in Liberalitas.

rows.label: qst105701_msg0014
rows.name: Please look into case for Nilny!

rows.label: qst105701_msg0101
rows.name:
Never thought that such thing emerge
from among Bahn's Mom letters.

rows.label: qst105701_msg0102
rows.name:
Most kind Nopon would close
treasure trove softly and walk away
after reading such contents...
